    <item>
      <title>无人驾驶拖拉机正在重塑农业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-27/driverless-tractors-are-reshaping-agriculture-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[约翰迪尔已经开始销售无需驾驶员的拖拉机。随着农场数量不断减少，行业面临变革压力，新机器应运而生。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-27/driverless-tractors-are-reshaping-agriculture-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 15:37:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>警方查获涉嫌运往网上零售商的赃物</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/california-police-seize-suspected-stolen-goods-bound-for-amazon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[警方突袭了南加州的一个仓库，仓库里堆满了疑似被盗商品，警方称这些商品很可能最终流入亚马逊公司和其他零售商运营的网上市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/california-police-seize-suspected-stolen-goods-bound-for-amazon</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 14:24:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>“已到极限”：墨西哥电网瘫痪威胁近岸外包</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/-at-its-limit-mexico-s-buckling-grid-threatens-nearshoring</link>
      <description><![CDATA[蓬勃发展的经济和极端的气温使墨西哥各地的电网濒临崩溃，而随着每个新的工业园区和仓库的建立，危机变得更加严重。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/-at-its-limit-mexico-s-buckling-grid-threatens-nearshoring</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>团体称拜登应结束 Verisign .Com 域名垄断</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/biden-administration-should-end-verisign-monopoly-over-com-domain-groups-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[反垄断人士表示，拜登政府应该迫使威瑞信公司 (Verisign Inc.) 参与竞争性投标，以维持以 .com 结尾的网站注册，该公司在过去十年中将价格提高了 70%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/biden-administration-should-end-verisign-monopoly-over-com-domain-groups-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 10:37:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Verizon、AT&T 移动用户面临海外连接问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/verizon-users-abroad-say-they-can-t-connect-to-mobile-network</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国主要电信公司的客户（包括 AT&amp;T Inc.、T Mobile US Inc. 和 Verizon Communications Inc.）均报告称，​​他们在国外时遇到了网络连接问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/verizon-users-abroad-say-they-can-t-connect-to-mobile-network</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 10:03:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃及耗资 100 亿美元的风电场有望于 2026 年破土动工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/egypt-s-10-billion-wind-farm-is-poised-to-break-ground-in-2026</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家参与建设的公司表示，世界上最大的风电场之一将于 2026 年 3 月在埃及开始建设，因为炎热夏季的严重停电凸显了这个北非国家的能源需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/egypt-s-10-billion-wind-farm-is-poised-to-break-ground-in-2026</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 09:20:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
